    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine sancte [et] individue trinitatis. <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/173">Otto</persName> divina favente clementia <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">imperator</rs> augustus. Noverit omnium fidelium
                        sancte [dei] ecclesie nostrorumque presentium scilicet ac futurorum
                        industria, <persName key="#fidelisOf" ref="#people/650">Vitalis Candianus
                            Veneticus </persName>noster <rs key="#fidelisOf">fidelis</rs>
                        suppliciter nostre pietatis exorasse clementiam, quatenus quandam <rs
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >curtem iuris regni nostri</rs> que dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Rivers #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Mountains #Curtes #Forests #Fisheries #Mills #Cereals #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Wood #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            ref="#places/949"><geogName
                                key="#Rivers #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Mountains #Curtes #Forests #Fisheries #Mills #Cereals #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Wood #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                                ref="#estates/546">Musestre</geogName></placeName>, videlicet in <rs
                            key="#Comitatus">comitatu</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Comitatus" ref="#places/13"><geogName key="#Comitatus"
                                ref="#estates/125">Tarvisiensi</geogName></placeName>, cum
                            <placeName
                            key="#Forests #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                                ><rs
                                key="#Forests #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals"
                                >silva</rs> de Uiualda</placeName> seu etiam cum <placeName
                            key="#Rivers #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Mountains #Villas #Forests #Fisheries #Mills #Cereals #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Wood #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Census #Aldius #Slave"
                            ref="#places/950"><geogName
                                key="#Rivers #Marshes/lagoons/tombolos #Mountains #Villas #Forests #Fisheries #Mills #Cereals #Wine #Fruits/vegetables #Wood #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals #Aldius #Slave"
                                ref="#estates/547"><rs
                                    key="#Villas #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals"
                                    >villa</rs> nuncupata Barbarana </geogName></placeName>et cum
                        universis ad eam <rs key="#Curtes">curtem</rs> pertinentibus vel
                        aspicientibus nec non et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >pratum</rs> pertinentem de ipso comitatu Tarvisiense quod dicitur
                            <placeName
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Hay/fodder #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >Regale</placeName> et <rs key="#Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            >piscationem</rs> in <rs key="#Rivers">fluvio</rs> qui dicitur Syle per
                        huius nostri precepti paginam iure proprietario Uitali Candiano fideli
                        nostro concedere dignaremur. Cuius petitionibus aures nostre pietatis
                        inflectentes iam dictam curtem que dicitur Musestre adiacentem in comitatu
                        Tarvisiense cum silva de Uiualda seu etiam cum villa nuncupata Barbarana et
                        cum universis ad pretaxatam curtem pertinentibus vel eis aspicientibus, cum
                            <rs key="#Cereals">terris aratoriis </rs>seu <rs key="#Wine">vineis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Hay/fodder">pratis pascuis </rs><rs key="#Forests">silvis</rs>
                        venationibus <rs key="#Wood">saletis</rs> sationibus <rs key="#Census"
                            >pensionibus</rs>
                        <rs key="#Rent_in_kind">redditibus</rs> sterpaticis <rs
                            key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos">paludibus</rs><rs key="#Rivers"> aquis
                            aquarumque decursibus</rs>
                        <rs key="#Mills">molendinis</rs>
                        <rs key="#Fisheries">piscationibus</rs>
                        <rs key="#Slave">servis et ancillis </rs><rs key="#Aldius">aldionibus et
                            aldiabus</rs>
                        <rs key="#Mountains">montibus</rs> planiciebus <rs key="#Fruits/vegetables"
                            >arboribus pomiferis</rs> seu cum omnibus que dici vel nominari possunt
                        ad prefatam curtem pertinentibus, nec non et pratum pertinentem de predicto
                        comitatu Tarvisiense quod dicitur pratum Regale et piscationem in fluvio
                        Syle, sicut actenus ad nostram imperialem pertinuit partem, in iam dicto
                        Vitali Candiano Uenetico fideli nostro per hanc nostre donationis seu
                        concessionis paginam <rs key="#Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure">iure
                            proprietario</rs> concedimus et donamus et [de] nostro iure et dominio
                        in eius ius et dominium omnino largimur et delegamus ad habendum tenendum
                        vendendum donandum commutandum et pro anima iudicandum, faciendo exinde
                        quicquid eius decreverit animus, nostra plenissima largitate, omnium hominum
                        contradictione remota. Si quis igitur hoc nostre donationis seu concessionis
                        preceptum infringere aut contradicere aliquo tempore quesierit, sciat se
                        compositurum <rs key="#Penalty">auri optimi libras centum</rs>, medietatem
                            <rs key="#Camera_regis">camere nostre</rs> et medietatem iam dicto
                        Uitali Candiano Uenetico suisque heredibus vel cui ipse dederit aut habere
                        concesserit. Quod ut verius credatur et diligentius ab omnibus observetur,
                        manu propria roborantes de anulo nostro subter insigniri iussimus. Signum
                        domni Ottonis (M.) magni et invictissimi imperatoris augusti. <persName
                            key="#Chancellor"><name ref="Liutgerius">Liutgerius</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Chancellor">cancellarius</rs> advicem <persName
                            key="#Archchancellor #Bishops" ref="#people/1303">Uuidonis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Bishops">episcopi</rs> [et] <rs key="#Archchancellor"
                            >archicancellarii</rs> recognovit. Data VII. kal. septembris anno
                        dominice incarnationis DCCCCLXIII, indictione VI, anno imperii magni Ottonis
                        imperatoris augusti II; actum in <placeName key="#Mountains #Fortress"
                            ref="#places/1861"><rs key="#Mountains">monte</rs> Feretri ad <rs
                                key="#Fortress">petram</rs> sancti Leonis</placeName>.</ab>
                </div>
